premise_source_doc_sentence: Felix Arvid Ulf Kjellberg  (  -LSB- ˈʃɛlbɜːrɡ -RSB- , -LSB- ˈfeːlɪks ² ɕɛlːˌbærj -RSB- ; born on 24 October 1989  )  , better known by his online pseudonym PewDiePie  (  -LSB- ˈpjuːdipaɪ -RSB-  )  , is a Swedish web-based comedian and video producer .
